  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    ViewObserver
    Interface listener for Views and ArchiveController.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    AboutView
    Handles the about view.
    AdminInfoView
    Handles the administrative information view.
    ArchiveController
    Serves as the link between the views and the models.
    ArchiveModel
    Holds all data about the archive and its relevant utility functions.
    ArkadeModel
    Class for handling and parsing the Arkade testreport html file.
    Main
    Serves as entrypoint for the application.
    MainView
    Handles the main view, which is the front page.
    ReportModel
    Class for handling report document configurations.
    ReportModel.Chapter
    Class for handling every ChapterList
    ReportModel.Content  
    ReportModel.HeadersData
    Class for handling headers that are fetched from document.
    ReportModel.SectionList
    Handles all the sections in a certain chapter
    SettingsModel
    Contains configuration utility functions and the properties object.
    SettingsView
    Handles the settings view.
    TestSettingsView
    Handles the test settings view.
    TestView
    Handles the test view.
    ThirdPartiesModel
    Contains multiple methods to run different third party tools to test the archive.
    Views
    Super class for all views.
